{"tid":1848223,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［正視聽］林奠嘅所謂「封關」只係想阻止醫護罷工","createTime":"2020-01-28T10:49:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-28T12:05:32.000Z","uid":74083,"like":34,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"b27fd8f0bb5ef4ca0b8fece4839fb2b806b6d1eb","tid":1848223,"uid":74083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T10:49:08.000Z","msg":"呢幾日醫護吹雞要罷工<br />\n已經有接近萬人加入工會<br />\n嚮應行動<br />\n醫護罷工根本係最強嘅核彈令正苦跪低<br />\n<br />\n林奠都心知不妙<br />\n早兩日話唔封關今日又改口話星期4封<br />\n咁樣早你一步封關<br />\n令你罷工都會名不正言不順<br />\n<br />\n但大家搞清楚<br />\n所謂封關只係局部性封關<br />\n主要陸路出入口都唔會封<br />\n根本就唔係封關<br />\n但就營造到正苦已經做野阻止中國人落嚟<br />\n你班醫護就乖乖地做前線condom 啦<br />\n<br />\n但醒目嘅你知道個正苦根本唔可信<br />\n一切都係謊言<br />\n<br />\n所以醫護人員要做嘅就係繼續堅持原則<br />\n要求正苦確實「全面」封關<br />\n阻止中國人落嚟傳播病菌<br />\n否則就實行罷工行動"},{"pid":"6641b6767b570475e272fa3696d4bc6ec4c5fddb","tid":1848223,"uid":52090,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T10:49:40.000Z","msg":"醫護工會必須發繄急聲明，政府拒絕 [真封關]，用 [假封關] 黎打輿論戰<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1844351/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1844351/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Kf2r8ci.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKf2r8ci.png&h=0786f2cd&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"131ff84d4ad90ac7e73e1d1b5e50edd9cd5f9d34","tid":1848223,"uid":143124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T10:50:06.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4c703771266410f6970e4fdd46398c3c1cb4c52d","tid":1848223,"uid":258696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T10:50:18.000Z","msg":"罷硬 屌佢老母臭閪<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n送頭？不了"},{"pid":"e5f057f240facf28426790b69c8bc691bf7781a2","tid":1848223,"uid":122275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T10:50:23.000Z","msg":"罷佢老母西"},{"pid":"3ed8db5123fbc6e649b0d05e537b20ae25a6338a","tid":1848223,"uid":21139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score